room_title: Escape room "The Burning Castle" by Time to Escape in Denver
room_description: Our founder, Dr. R. K. Adler, has gone missing. We believe he is trapped in 15th century Transylvania in the castle of the infamous Vlad the Impaler. Your mission is to travel back in time and search for evidence of Adler’s whereabouts. Beware though… there may be more danger in this castle than just Vlad himself!
